            ],
            "parameters": {
                "width": 656,
                "height": 496,
                "content": "## \ud83d\udcca AI-Powered HighLevel \u2192 Google Sheets Sync & Daily HTML Report Workflow (GPT-4o + Gmail)  \nThis workflow syncs CRM opportunities from HighLevel into Google Sheets and automatically creates a daily HTML summary email using GPT-4o.\n\n### \ud83d\udd39 Workflow Overview\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Fetch opportunities from HighLevel CRM  \n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Validate records for completeness  \n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Extract & normalize key fields  \n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Update opportunities in Google Sheets  \n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Merge all data into a single array  \n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Use GPT-4o to create an HTML sales summary table  \n7\ufe0f\u20e3 Email the final report to the sales team  \n\n### \ud83d\udd39 Tools & Integrations\n- HighLevel CRM \u2192 Opportunity data source  \n- Google Sheets \u2192 Data storage  \n- Azure OpenAI (GPT-4o) \u2192 AI report generator  \n- Gmail \u2192 Automated daily summary delivery  \n- JavaScript Nodes \u2192 Data cleaning and transformation  \n"
            },
            "typeVersion": 1
        },
        {
            "id": "c5053949-91d9-499b-b9fa-09c4ad533c0c",
            "name": "Sticky Note1",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "position": [
                -704,
                -304
            ],
            "parameters": {
                "color": 7,
                "height": 544,
                "content": "## \ud83d\udd17 Fetch Opportunities from HighLevel CRM  \nPulls recent opportunity data (limit: 5 by default) from your HighLevel CRM account.  \nIncludes contact details, company, source, and stage info.  \nThis is the main data entry point.\n"
            },
            "typeVersion": 1
        },
        {
